@node "ROSWELL PAGE" "GROUND ZERO SOFTWARE PRODUCTION."
                                @{bg fill}ROSWELL PAGE@{bg back}

"In 1947 the people of Roswell witnessed the crash of a UFO in the
 surrounding desert, the US government threatened residents of this small
 town to keep quiet. The government claimed the object was simply a
 new type of secret weather balloon, and not the metalic alien ship and
 dead and living extraterrestial creatures everyone else believes to be 
 case. Books and films been produced based on this conspiracy, there are
 still many living witnesses today. Apparently the confidential film
 footage of the Roswell alien autopsy was obtained from top security
 Nasa archives, but whether of not this will be shown on national 
 television is another matter".

