@node "GROUND ZERO PAGE" "GROUND ZERO SOFTWARE PRODUCTION"
 WHAT IS GROUND ZERO SOFTWARE 
 ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

Besides compiling popular themed disks and productions like Aliens
Confidential Multimedia, Ground Zero Software is a long time running PD
library with over 3 years of experience.

 If you haven't already seen our full page advertisements, then look in
Amiga Format for our latest up to date list of PD disk titles and CD ROMS,
including GROUND ZERO SOFTWARE's own CD ROM titles for Amiga, PC and
Macintosh computer platforms.

 LOOK OUT FOR:

 ZOOM CD
 ~~~~~~~
 The best PD and Shareware from Demember 1994 to June 1995. Over 500 
 megabytes (over one gigabyte when expanded) of Amiga software from 2
 top libraries; Ground Zero Software and Active Software. 
 Custom interface extracts software straight to floppies, ready to run
 and no hassles.
 Workbench 2.0+ required to run interface.


 PHANTASMAGORIA TEXTURES AND BACKGROUDS
 ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
 Hundreds of royalty free and completely original photographic images for
 use as textures within raytracing, backgrounds for colour dtp and 
 backgrounds for video titling. This is not your usual image CD, it has
 taken a period of 5 years work by professionals to compile this
 collection. Includes images of marble, stone, animal fur, metals, rippling
 water, clouds, fire and many other subjects that you simply can't find
 elsewhere. Includes tutorials on how to make the best use of the textures
 for  raytracing. The images come in the form of 24 bit Jpeg's, 256 colour
 Gifs and a selection in IFF format, plus image programmes for conversion
 and processing. 
 For Amiga, PC and MAC computer systems.


 FUTURE TITLES
 ~~~~~~~~~~~~~
 We have a whole host planned, keep your eyes open for more great titles
 from Ground Zero Software.
@endnode

@node "INTRODUCTION" "GROUND ZERO SOFTWARE PRODUCTION"

 Welcome to Aliens Confidential Multimedia. After the success of the first
two 1 disk Aliens Confidential titles, we were able to source enough
material to fill this impressive nine disk title, with 200 text files and
several megabytes of images.

 Aliens Confidential is the most comprehensive study of the UFO and Alien
phenomena especially put together for the Amiga computer. 

 Since it is impossible to prove that all the images and text files are
genuine we can only guarantee we have done our upmost to use as reliable
sources as possible.
@endnode

